<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="delay-v">delay <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'leɪ/    美 /dɪ'leɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-put-off">1.★ <strong>耽误；延误；推迟 (put off)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ll lose your chance if you delay. 
如果拖延你就会失去机会。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My flight was delayed because of the heavy rain. 
我乘坐的航班因为大雨而延误了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>delay doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He delayed telling her the news, waiting for the right moment. 
他迟迟没有把这消息告诉她，他在等待适当的时机。</p></div></div>